flowchart TD

User[User Question]

User --> NLParse[Natural Language Input]

NLParse --> EntityDetect[Entity Detection]

EntityDetect --> EntityResolver[Entity Resolver]

EntityResolver --> ContextBuilder[Context Builder]

ContextBuilder --> SemanticRetrieval[Semantic Retrieval<br>Vector Search]

SemanticRetrieval --> Planner

Planner[LLM Planner<br>NL → QuerySpec]

Planner --> QuerySpec[Structured QuerySpec]

QuerySpec --> Validator[QuerySpec Validator]

Validator --> CostGuard[Query Cost Guardrail]

CostGuard --> DatasetResolver[Dataset Resolver]

DatasetResolver --> SQLBuilder[SQL Builder AST]

SQLBuilder --> SQL[Deterministic SQL]

SQL --> Database[(Database Execution)]

Database --> Result[Query Result]

Result --> Formatter[Response Formatter]

Formatter --> Response[User Answer]
